        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the always-behind loop. The script targets the loop where the to-do list is running, the email is unanswered, the laundry is one cycle behind, and other people's lives appear to be in order from the outside. The catching-up that never catches up."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "text": "Even though I feel like I'm always behind, I deeply and completely accept myself." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "text": "Even though the list keeps growing and I keep running, I deeply and completely accept myself." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "text": "Even though everyone else seems to be ahead, I deeply and completely accept myself." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I'm behind before the day has even started." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " The list runs in my head before I'm out of bed." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I keep thinking I should be further along." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " Other people's lives look in order from where I'm sitting." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I'm scared that catching up is the whole life now." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I'm tired of running to stand still." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " The pressure to catch up sits in my chest." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I'm here, and that has to count for something." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I give myself permission to start the day where I am." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " The list will keep. It always does." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " Where I am is where I am, and that is enough to work with." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I am not behind anyone. I am here, on my own path." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I choose one next thing, then the next, and that is plenty." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I let the pace slow without anything falling over." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " My pace is allowed to be mine." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" },
                  { "type": "text", "text": " I am exactly here, and exactly here is workable." }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Tap each round three times before moving on. Total: about five minutes."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The tapping framework is Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s. The eight-point sequence follows Craig's standard shorthand. The always-behind theme and the specific script are original to the homemade.education library, written for the audience this section serves."
